00:58:25.840 --> 00:58:30.913
which is very rational,
but then he is undoing it with

00:58:30.913 --> 00:58:35.510
something that stands between
madness and love,

00:58:35.510 --> 00:58:36.480
and that's the imagination.
 

00:58:36.480 --> 00:58:39.900
See the connection?
 

00:58:39.900 --> 00:58:41.150
Okay.
 

